unk_c820299.value:
--Start Duo Tormented Shrine Encounter and make invulnerable
	
	for i, idShrine in ipairs(T_SPN_SHRINES) do
			Hydra.ActorEnable(idShrine)
			Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(idShrine, "Banshee")
				--TEMP Banshee prop
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idShrine, true)
				--Play Eruption VFX
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idShrine, EFF_SHRINE_EXP)
				--Play Eruption SFX
			Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idShrine, SFX_ERUPTION)
			Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idShrine, true)
	end
	
--Woordwraith Defense Bubble spawn and activation
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(T_SPN_SPIRITS) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idSpawner)
	end
	
	Hydra.EventSend("SpiritBubble")

unk_98d4504.value:
--Disable Spawners
	T_SPN_SPIRITS = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Scos_Hills_DuoBansheeSpawners")
	
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(T_SPN_SPIRITS) do
		Hydra.ActorDisable(idSpawner)
	end

--Despawn Prefab
	Hydra.Wait(2.0)
	Hydra.ActorFlagDynamicPrefabGroupForDespawn(idSelf)
	
Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

--Activate Spirit Bubble effect

	for i, idShrine in ipairs(T_SPN_SHRINES) do
		tBubbles[idShrine] = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idShrine, EFF_SPIRIT_BUBBLE, true)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

--Activate Woodwraiths ropes
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorSpawned)then
		tRopes[idActorSpawned] = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idActorSpawned, LOC_SPIRIT_ROPE, EFF_SPIRIT_ROPE, true)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

--Remove Woodwraith ropes
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorKilled)then
		Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idActorKilled, tRopes[idActorKilled])
	end
end

unk_98d4504.value:
--Deactivate Spirit Bubble effect and make vulnerable
	for i, idShrine in ipairs(T_SPN_SHRINES) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idShrine) then
			Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idShrine, tBubbles[idShrine])
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idShrine, EFF_SHRINE_EXP)
			Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idShrine, false)
		end
	end

--Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()
